export const projectsData = [
    {
        id: 1,
        projectName: ' PMC Grievance Management Portal ',
        projectDesc: 'College Project - This project aims to build a a web-based platform for managing grievances lodged with the Pune Municipal Corporation (PMC).',

        image: one
    },
    {
        id: 2,
        projectName: 'Gross Primary Prediction (GPP) Prediction',
        projectDesc: 'MITACS GRI Projct - This project aims to predict GPP using EVI, Solar Shortwave Radiation, Precipitation Level and Temperature for the Kishtwar region in Jammu and Kashmir.',
        tags: ['CatBoost', 'XGBoost', 'SVM', 'Random Forest', 'Python'],
        image: two
    },
    {
        id: 3,
        projectName: ' Map Amazon Deforestation for SDG 15.3',
        projectDesc: 'MITACS GRI Projct - Developed and evaluated predictive models using UNet and LSTM networks for mapping and predicting deforestation in the Amazon Rainforest and further analyzed their significance in achieving SDG15.3.',

        image: three

    {
        id: 4,
        projectName: 'GrainLog',
        projectDesc: 'College Project - GrainLog is an innovative agricultural project aimed at addressing the significant problem of food grain wastage, by enabling smart monitoring of granary and predicting the shelf life of the grains.',

        image: four
    },
    {
        id: 5,
        projectName: 'Forearm Bone Fracture Detection Using DenseNet',
        projectDesc: 'Research Project - This project aims to leverage DenseNet-169 to enhance the accuracy of detecting forearm bone fractures, achieving a notable test accuracy of 76% and an AUC of 0.835.',

        image: five
    },
    {
        id: 6,
        projectName: 'NeuroSight: Brain Tumour Detection Using Deep Learning',
        projectDesc: 'Research Project - This project aims to compare the effectiveness of five different machine learning models - InceptionNetV3, AlexNet, Multilayer Perceptron, ResNet-50, and VGG16 - in classifying brain tumors using MRI.',

        image: six
    },
    {
        id: 7,
        projectName: 'Price Prediction of Commodities',
        projectDesc: 'METI Project - I used LSTM to predict the price of the commodities as directed by LTID Co. Ltd. through the METI Government of Japan Internship Program.',
        tags: ['LSTM', 'Machine Learning', 'Prediction', 'Agriculture'],
        image: seven
    },
    {
        id: 8,
        projectName: 'Demand Prediction of Commodities',
        projectDesc: 'METI Project - I performed a comparative analysis of Random Forest and LSTM to predict the demand of the commodities as directed by LTID Co. Ltd. through the METI Government of Japan Internship Program.',
        tags: ['LSTM', 'Machine Learning', 'Prediction', 'Agriculture', 'Random Forest'],
        image: eight
    },
]
